 Kira Hollis was diagnosed with borderline personality disorder three years ago after a lengthy battle with depression and body dysmorphia .
She had been self-harming and experienced outbursts - and at just 6st , she was deemed clinically underweight .
Doctors had ordered the 27-year-old to go to the gym to gain some weight .
Ms Hollis says bodybuilding changed her life and gave her the confidence to overcome her depression .